serviceReviews.title: Let's build only with mee6 and discord
serviceReviews.text: Really appreciate the assistance that mee6 provides. Easy instructions and another of potential if we keep strict development guidelines. And continue to keep in mind the mission statement for discord communities.  Let's keep discord a free and safe place by staying with the developers and contributers we have had since day one and we can create intuitive bots that are for helping individuals create productive and positive  environments
